featured_reviews.review_text: Ask the masjid address from locals, the map may confuse you..

featured_reviews.review_id:
The Jama Masjid of Kalka is near Railway station opposite Railway Officers club.

It is a very old masjid built during Mughal times and the same has been re-constructed in the present shape.

The timing for Juma prayers is at 1:30 pm.
